Details:
Extrapolations from small-scale, short-term studies to estimate country-wide annual impacts. They applied conservative assumptions to offset this upscaling bias (e.g. no indirect and non-market costs estimated). This estimation for T. fuscum sums the costs for annual timber sales (spruce), annual domestic exports and spruce pulp.

